<br>
One possible argument (I would think) is that our defense is less effective than other light tanks. Our Evade 1 doesn't bring defense up to their level. One way to fix this without throwing things out of balance would be to give Mercs Avoid Pain. This is a nice RA but hardly one that's so powerful it would throw classes out of balance by having it.<br>
